3. wipe.rs, AFTER the existing scan wait (after line 34) and BEFORE spawn_blocking, add a bounded wait that mirrors the scan one:
   use std::sync::atomic::Ordering;
   let mut waited = 0u32;
   while face_cluster_active.load(Ordering::Acquire) && waited < 100 {
